CRM Analytics Settings

CRM Analytics settings include a preference setting for event logs, Developer Mode, and links to app information.
Send Event Logs: Option to send event logs automatically from your default email address to Salesforce.
Developer Mode: This setting enables features for dashboard designers, including notifications about auto-formatting when dashboards open. When Developer Mode is on, the designer control appears in the lower left corner of the dashboard (). Tap it to set Developer Mode to show widget names.
